= Shoe_vie

* http://github.com/maxdevel/shoe_vie/wikis
* mailto:

== DESCRIPTION:

Inspired from simple-video and simple-downloader samples to play with events and video.

A simple Shoes movie downloader, player, manager...

== FEATURES:

GUI usage

1) Provide a movie URL in "Url:", i.e:
http://whytheluckystiff.net/o..e/adventure_time.flv
(which is the default. Better another URL)
2) Provide in "Name to save:" the movie's name to save.
2a) Providing a name of a local movie in "Name to save:" without a download URL serve to play it.
3) Click the "Download" button. The movie shows only after a bit of download (clicking play before, of course).
3a) A progress represent the download progress.
3b) A status shows the download phases.
4) When playing, a progress represent the movie time.
4a) A time status represente the seconds elapsed.
5) A "Controls" bar allow to play, pause, stop, hide, show blahblah.

== VISION:

== MORE INFORMATION:

== INSTALL

Install Shoes

http://shoooes.net/downloads

or

http://github.com/why/shoes/tree/master

Add shoes to your PATH

By now, just use:

$ shoes shoevie.rb

Start knowing about Shoes

http://github.com/why/shoes/wikis
http://shoooes.net/
http://help.shoooes.net/
http://shoooes.net/tutorial/
http://newwws.shoooes.net/

